			<p><span style="font-weight:bold;"> Title:</span> Cardiovascular Magnetic Resonance Imaging: An Emerging Field in Clinical Practice</p>
			<p><span style="font-weight:bold;"> Speaker:</span> Dr. Mehdi Hedjazi Moghari, Research Fellow at Harvard Medical Center</p>
			<p><span style="font-weight:bold;"> Date:</span> Monday November 12, 2012</p>
			<p><span style="font-weight:bold;"> Time:</span> 2PM - 3PM</p>
			<p><span style="font-weight:bold;"> Location:</span> McConnell Engineering Building, room 603</p>
			<p>Pizza and pop will be served.<br  /></p>
<p><span style="color:red">There will be 15 minutes of networking and socializing prior to the talk</span></p>
			<div id="comments_0007" class="comments">
